quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,BY THE snorting war steeds
  100,2,which strike fire with their hoofs
  100,3,as they gallop to the raid at morn
  100,4,and with a trail of dust
  100,5,cleave a massed army
  100,6,Man is ungrateful to his Lord
  100,7,To this he himself shall bear witness
  100,8,He loves riches with all his heart
  100,9,But is he not aware that when the dead are thrown out from their graves
  100,10,and their once hidden thoughts are laid bare
  100,11,their Lord will on that day have full knowledge of them all